<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Jonathan D. Gonzalez Gaspar — Marketing Strategist</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com"/>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;0,900;1,400;1,700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
  :root {
    --ink: #0F0E0C;
    --paper: #F7F4EE;
    --cream: #EDE8DC;
    --rust: #C4480A;
    --rust-light: #F0D5C8;
    --gold: #B8934A;
    --muted: #7A7669;
    --border: rgba(15,14,12,0.12);
    --font-display: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
    --font-body: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    --font-mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 1.25rem 3rem;
    background: rgba(247,244,238,0.92);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .nav-logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none;
  }

  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--rust); }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  #home {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    padding-top: 80px;
  }

  .hero-left {
    padding: 6rem 3rem 4rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.0;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-name em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.5rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--ink);
    max-width: 42ch;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--rust);
    border-color: var(--rust);
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: 2px solid var(--border);
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }

  .hero-right {
    padding: 6rem 3rem 4rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0;
  }

  .stat-item {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-right: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .stat-item:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; }
  .stat-item:nth-last-child(-n+2) { border-bottom: none; }

  .stat-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .stat-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .hero-tagline {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
    background: white;
  }

  .hero-tagline p {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* ── SECTION BASICS ── */
  section { padding: 6rem 0; }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-title em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 3rem;
  }

  /* ── ABOUT ── */
  #about {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  #about .section-label { color: var(--gold); }
  #about .section-title { color: var(--paper); }
  #about .section-title em { color: var(--gold); }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.8fr 1.4fr 0.9fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .about-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.8);
  }

  .about-body p + p { margin-top: 1.25rem; }

  .about-body strong { color: var(--paper); font-weight: 500; }

  .about-sidebar {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-fact {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(247,244,238,0.12);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .about-fact-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-fact-value {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--paper);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── WORK ── */
  #work { background: var(--paper); }

  .work-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    align-items: end;
  }

  .work-desc {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .case-studies {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .case-study {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr auto;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    align-items: start;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .case-study:hover { background: var(--cream); padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem; margin: 0 -1rem; }

  .case-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--rust-light);
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 0.25rem;
  }

  .case-content { flex: 1; }

  .case-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    background: var(--rust-light);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .case-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .case-desc {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 60ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .case-results {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .case-result {
    text-align: left;
  }

  .case-result-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--rust);
    display: block;
  }

  .case-result-label {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  .case-services {
    text-align: right;
    min-width: 160px;
  }

  .case-service-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .case-service-item {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  /* ── RESEARCH ── */
  #research {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .research-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .research-col-title {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .pub-item {
    padding: 1.25rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .pub-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .pub-meta {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .pub-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .badge-published { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }
  .badge-prep { background: var(--gold); color: white; }
  .badge-conf { background: var(--rust-light); color: var(--rust); }

  .conf-item {
    padding: 0.9rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .conf-title {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.4;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .conf-meta {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ── THINKING ── */
  #thinking { background: var(--paper); }

  .essay-card {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 2fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding: 3rem;
    background: var(--cream);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--rust);
  }

  .essay-meta { }

  .essay-date {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .essay-category {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    background: var(--rust-light);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .essay-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .essay-read {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--rust);
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rust);
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .essay-content { }

  .essay-excerpt {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .essay-excerpt p + p { margin-top: 1rem; }

  .essay-excerpt strong {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--rust);
  }

  /* Essay modal */
  .modal-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed; inset: 0; z-index: 200;
    background: rgba(15,14,12,0.7);
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .modal-overlay.open { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; justify-content: center; }

  .modal-box {
    background: var(--paper);
    max-width: 680px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: auto;
    padding: 3rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .modal-close {
    position: absolute; top: 1.5rem; right: 1.5rem;
    background: none; border: none; font-size: 1.5rem; cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--muted);
    transition: color 0.2s;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }

  .modal-close:hover { color: var(--rust); }

  .modal-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .modal-byline {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .modal-body {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .modal-body p + p { margin-top: 1.25rem; }
  .modal-body h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.75rem;
  }

  .modal-body strong { font-weight: 500; color: var(--rust); }

  /* ── CONTACT ── */
  #contact {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-align: center;
  }

  #contact .section-label { color: var(--gold); }
  #contact .section-title { color: var(--paper); }
  #contact .section-title em { color: var(--gold); }

  .contact-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.65);
    max-width: 50ch;
    margin: 1rem auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(247,244,238,0.2);
    color: var(--paper);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .contact-link:hover {
    background: var(--rust);
    border-color: var(--rust);
  }

  .contact-divider {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--gold);
    margin: 3rem auto;
  }

  .contact-detail {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.5);
    line-height: 2;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  footer {
    background: #070706;
    padding: 1.5rem 3rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .footer-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.4);
  }

  .footer-copy {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: rgba(247,244,238,0.25);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  }


  .about-photo-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/5;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    filter: grayscale(20%);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  .fade-up {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(24px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }

  .fade-up.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
    .nav-links { gap: 1.5rem; }
    #home { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 5rem 1.5rem 3rem; }
    .hero-right { padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; } .research-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
    .work-intro { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1rem; }
    .case-study { grid-template-columns: 50px 1fr; }
    .case-services { display: none; }
    .essay-card { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .container { padding: 0 1.5rem; }
    section { padding: 4rem 0; }
    .hero-name { font-size: 2.8rem; }
    .modal-box { padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#home" class="nav-logo">JDG</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
    <li><a href="#work">Work</a></li>
    <li><a href="#research">Research</a></li>
    <li><a href="#thinking">Thinking</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section id="home">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <p class="hero-eyebrow">Marketing Strategist · Austin, TX</p>
    <h1 class="hero-name">Jonathan<br/><em>Gonzalez</em><br/>Gaspar</h1>
    <p class="hero-title">Consumer Behaviorist & Brand Builder</p>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      I use clinical psychology training to do what most marketers can't — understand why people actually make decisions, then build brand strategy around it. Bilingual. Data-driven. Built to own the strategy room.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-cta">
      <a href="#work" class="btn-primary">View My Work</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-secondary">Let's Talk</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-right">
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">166%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Engagement growth driven for Icon Cinema</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">1.3M+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Content views generated across campaigns</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">25+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Customer discovery interviews conducted</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-number">294K</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Unique viewers reached through targeted content</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-tagline">
      <p>"Most marketers read about consumer psychology.<br/>I spent years practicing it."</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label fade-up">About</p>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-up">The story behind<br/><em>the strategy</em></h2>
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-photo-wrap">
        <img src="data:image/jpeg;base64," class="about-photo" alt="Jonathan D. Gonzalez Gaspar"/>
      </div>
            <div class="about-body fade-up">
        <p>
          Most marketing strategists learn consumer behavior from a textbook. I spent years sitting across from real people — understanding their fears, their motivations, the gap between what they say and what they actually do. That's not a credential. That's a completely different way of seeing an audience.
        </p>
        <p>
          My path wasn't linear. I trained as a clinical psychologist, earning my M.A. from Hofstra University and my M.S. from Angelo State, where I also taught research methods, published peer-reviewed work, and led National Science Foundation research into how people make decisions. Then I pivoted — deliberately — into marketing strategy, because I saw that the brands winning right now aren't just the ones with the biggest budgets. They're the ones that actually understand people.
